![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/41f617f4-3f7f-4acf-a9a5-93a912aa33aa/ep230.jpg)

While the Arrowverse is picking out their caskets, the Marvel shows on Disney+ can't seem to miss. The same holds true for their latest entry into the television genre, Moon Knight, starring Oscar Isaac in the titular role. It's not your average show folks, but what did WE think? Was it Aces or Later Gaters for the vengeful vigilante? What IS A MAN WITHOUT LOVE!?? Some or none of these questions will be answered in this spoiler-filled review of Moon Knight S1!  
  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

  
